so it was easy to see
what was happening.

395
00:32:40,825 --> 00:32:43,828
Bobby Lembeck被分割到了左边
Bobby Lembeck got separated
to the left.

396
00:32:43,828 --> 00:32:45,489
Mavole跟在他的后面
Mavole went after him.

397
00:32:46,531 --> 00:32:49,830
当他跟上Bobby时敌人已经确定了他们的位置
