inning for them...

1429
01:52:41,421 --> 01:52:44,824
打败美国的最好机会
the greatest foothold
they will ever have in this country.

1430
01:52:44,824 --> 01:52:50,430
他们却如此回报我，把你的灵魂带走，
给我一具空壳
And they paid me back
by taking your soul away from you.

1431
01:52:50,430 --> 01:52:53,266
